  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下零售客户忠诚度系统的整体架构。我想从核心模块Retail_CustomerLoyalty出发，看看它如何与其他系统交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解您想以Retail_CustomerLoyalty作为顶层节点。那么它主要向下延伸出哪些大的分支呢？我注意到可能涉及客户管理和订单相关的能力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，核心节点应该分出两条主线：一条是B分支，继续深化客户忠诚度本身的子能力；另一条C分支，对接Retail_OrderManagement订单管理系统。这两条线的业务权重相当。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "B",
        "C",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，A节点向下分出B和C。B还是Retail_CustomerLoyalty的细化，C是订单管理。我先把这个骨架画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "骨架已建好。现在B节点下面需要展开哪些具体子系统？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "B这条线要放五个关键子模块。首先是B1，Retail_PointOfSale，也就是销售终端系统，这是客户接触的第一现场。然后是B2和B3，都指向Retail_OrderManagement，分别是订单创建和订单追踪两个细分能力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B1",
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "B2",
        "B3",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有B4和B5，都是Retail_Inventory库存系统的接口，一个管实时库存查询，一个管库存锁定。这五个子节点都挂在B下面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B4",
        "B5",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，B下面挂B1到B5五个节点，分别对应POS终端、两个订单管理子能力、两个库存接口。我注意到B2和B3标签相同但实例不同，B4和B5也是类似处理，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B1",
        "B2",
        "B3",
        "B4",
        "B5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，业务上它们是同一系统的不同调用场景，需要分开标识。现在来看C分支，Retail_OrderManagement这条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "B分支的五个子节点已添加完毕。请继续讲C分支的结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B1",
        "B2",
        "B3",
        "B4",
        "B5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "C分支同样有五个子节点。C1是Retail_CouponSystem优惠券系统，这是订单结算时的关键能力。C2和C3都是Retail_PointOfSale，但一个是线下门店POS，一个是移动端POS，需要区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "C4要连回Retail_CustomerLoyalty，形成闭环，表示订单完成后积分反馈到忠诚度系统。C5是Retail_Inventory，订单对库存的扣减操作。",
