      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修复，B3现在正确指向Retail_OrderManagement。再检查一下C2和C3，两者都是Retail_PointOfSale，这个没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
