      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "C2和C3都是Retail_PointOfSale，正确。不过我想再确认一下C5，它到Retail_Inventory的连接，是表示订单扣减库存吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
